 Retail Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

Overview

This is my Power BI project based on the Sample Superstore dataset.  
I used Excel for cleaning and Power BI for building an interactive dashboard that shows sales, profit, and quantity performance across different regions, categories, and segments.

Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel → Data cleaning and transformation  
- Power BI → Data modeling, DAX measures, and visualization  

Dashboard Highlights
- KPIs: Total Sales, Total Profit, Orders, Quantity, and Profit Margin  
- Visuals: Sales by Category, Profit by Region, Monthly Sales Trend  
- Filters: Region, Category, and Segment slicers  

Key Insights
- Technology category drives the highest sales  
- East region contributes the most profit  
- Overall profit margin is around 13.5%  
- Consistent sales growth across months  

Files Included
- Retail_Sales_Dashboard.pbix – Power BI dashboard  
- Retail_Sales_Dashboard.xlsx – Cleaned dataset  
- Sample - Superstore.csv – Original raw data  


